[SN]TITLE[SN]
Election 2015: Audience sought for BBC Radio Scotland debate in Gordon

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Audience members are being sought for a BBC Radio Scotland hustings debate in Gordon in Aberdeenshire ahead of the General Election.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gordon is set to be one of the most high-profile seats in the General Election, which will be held on 7 May.
The programme will be recorded on the evening of Thursday 23 April at Thainstone, near Inverurie.
Anyone interested can contact northeastdebate@bbc.co.uk
